; RoomDispatchTable
;
; 34 × 16-bit function pointers for the per-room game handler dispatch.
; Indexed as table[room_mode × 2], accessed by the dispatcher at #R35314
; via JP (HL). Room modes 0-33 each map to a handler routine. Pairs of
; entries often share the same handler (modes 0-1, 4-5, etc.).
;
; Room mode → handler mapping:
;  0-1: #R35314  2-3: #R35338  4: #R35578  5: #R35448
;  6-12: #R35163 (RoomHandlerCommon)        13: #R35222
;  14-16: #R35448  17-19: #R35210  20-23: #R35448
;  24: #R35560  25-29: #R35382  30-31: #R35448  32: #R35449
;  33: #R35451
;
