; UpdateCrewAI
@ignoreua
;
; Assigns a new action to the first idle crew member. Scans the 7-entry crew
; data table at $7236 (IX+0 = action counter). If a crew member's counter is
; non-zero they are busy; the first one with counter = 0 gets a new action
; sourced from the ROM-traversal script. The action sets IX+3 (action state:
; 2=move, 3=wait, 5=investigate) and IX+0 (action timer). If no crew member
; is idle, returns immediately.
;
; Used by the routine at #R36457.
@label=UpdateCrewAI
c37018 PUSH IX       ; save caller's IX
@ignoreua
 37020 LD IX,29566   ; IX = crew data base ($7236, first 7-entry crew table)
 37024 XOR A         ; A = 0
 37025 CP (IX+0)     ; is crew member 0's action counter zero (idle)?
 37028 JR Z,37033    ; yes: assign new action at #R45721
 37030 POP IX        ; crew member busy: restore IX
 37032 RET           ; return without change
