; DrawIntroScreen
@ignoreua
;
; Draws and animates the Alien title screen. Clears the display, sets border
; to black, fills attributes (0 = black on black = hidden). Renders a 15×11
; tile grid: each byte of the tile map at #R40504 is a tile index; multiplied
; by 8 gives an offset into the 8-byte-per-tile bitmap array at #R62000
; (actually at #R62000 = #R62000 decimal, in the extra-data area loaded at #R60000).
; Tile rows are blitted column by column down into the display file. After
; drawing, loops animating colours until any key on row $F7FE is pressed.
;
; Used by the routine at #R36457.
@label=DrawIntroScreen
